2.1.3
- Added support for bootstrap.js button() method
- Added support for data-required, and title attributes for alert text
- Changed order for attribute fail over to determine which alert text to use first.

2.1.2
- Added support to check min and max length on string input fields
- Changed jQuery methods from .attr() to .prop() for proper boolean values

2.1.1
- Added class for fields w/ errors
- Updated inline documentation on JavaScript file
- Fixed bad syntax, and added missing escapes from RegExp

2.1.0
- Updated script to user jQuery and added support for jQuery UI
- Validates based on classes and field types
- Supports callback function
- Added validation for URL fields
- Added validation for step attribute in number and range fields
